      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/df86e7f0-07d3-11e4-92f3-5254006e85c2).  Ran 26 tests.  1 tests failed: ost-pools.",
